data.description: ***Open House Saturday Jan 27 2pm-5pm***Welcome home! This amazing property is the perfect balance of space, convenience and opportunity. Offering 4 bedrooms in addition to a dedicated office/flex room (with doors) and mother-in-law suite with a kitchenette, this home is sure to meet all your needs. Whether you have a large family, want lots of space to spread out or are looking to rent out the additional space, with this home, you can do it all! All bedrooms except one have brand new carpet, most of the home has been freshly painted. One of the standout features is the Florida room with a custom wood plank ceiling. Currently used as a game room but could easily be the perfect spot for morning coffee or relaxing after a long day. You might decide to keep it a game room because there is a ton of outdoor space to enjoy as well. Outside you will also find a detached garage that has doors on both the front and back that fully open. On the other side of the home you will find a full workshop for all your hobbies. Inside the living space features a fireplace and vaulted ceilings that only add to the spacious feel of this home. The kitchen shows off with ample counter and cabinet space in addition to a wall oven and gas cooktop. Mother-in-law suite could be rented short or long term. Roof was replaced in 2020 and the HVAC in 2019 making this home low maintenance. You really don’t want to miss out on this amazing home! Call for your private tour today.
